g 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/jack-white@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3844561" class="wp-caption-text">杰克·怀特（Jack White）在2024年演出。信用：斯科特·莱格托（Scott Legato）/盖蒂图片</figcaption></figure><p>“ <em>I was thinking about taking government subsidies and starting my own electric car company; Who&#39;s with me</em> ?”白色唱歌。 “ <em>I&#39;m thinking about not being elected.从不担任公职。从来没有服役一天，但以某种方式有权控制美国政府的部分地区；谁和我在一起？</em>透明</p><p>While still taking jabs at Musk, Jack White also manages to slide in a cheeky attack on Trump: “ <em>I&#39;m thinking about not being properly vetted by the Supreme Court or Congress, Just doing whatever the hell I want because some fucking bloated asshole orange fucking gorilla whose failed at every business he&#39;s ever ran wants me to be his golf cart partner.</em>透明</p><p>在下面查看严厉的表现的镜头。 </p><p><iframe title="杰克·怀特（Jack White）“公司”现场" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/er-mX2Ph6VE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这是杰克·怀特（Jack White）瞄准特朗普及其政府的最新情况。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-shares-blistering-attack-on-donald-trump-america-will-get-whatever-this-wannabe-dictator-wants-to-enact-3810360">Back in November, the White Stripes frontman reacted to Donald Trump&#39;s second electoral win</a> , launching a blistering post on social media: “Americans chose a known, obvious fascist and now America will get whatever this wannabe dictator wants to enact from here on in… It&#39;s absolutely dumbfounding that this con man succeeded in pulling the wool over so many Americans eyes not once, but twice.”</p><p> In August, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-tells-trump-campaign-dont-even-think-about-using-my-mu