hittaker-toxic-town-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841885" class="wp-caption-text">乔迪·惠特克（Jodie Whittaker</figcaption></figure><p> Netflix尚未宣布第二个赛季的任何计划。该节目最初被称为迷你剧，因此很不可能委托第二季。</p><p>在节目的四集中也结束了科比丑闻的故事，因此，除非完全解决另一个案件，否则该节目几乎没有理由继续进行。</p><h2>我现在应该看什么？</h2><p> The true story behind <em>Toxic Town</em> is often described as the English version of Erin Brockovich, a paralegal who was instrumental in building a case against Pacific Gas &amp; Electric Company in relation to water contamination in Hinkley, California.</p><p> This case was covered in the 2000 biographical film <em>Erin Brockovich</em> with Julia Roberts in the lead role, who won an Oscar for her performance.</p><p> As for other similar cases, 2019 film <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/dark-waters-review-mark-ruffalo-2600857"><em>Dark Waters</em></a> is a dramatised version of Robert Bilott&#39;s case against the chemical manufacturing company DuPont.由托德·海恩斯（Todd Haynes）执导的法律惊悚片由马克·鲁法洛（Mark Ruffalo）和安妮·海瑟薇（Anne Hathaway）主演。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/toxic-town-season-2-netflix-3845463">Will there be a &#39;Toxic Town&#39; season two?</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
