e-up-tickets-3835042">the stacked bill at Black Sabbath&#39;s final show in Birmingham&#39;s Villa Park</a> in July, which will also include <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Metallica">Metallica</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Slayer">Slayer</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Pantera">Pantera</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Lamb-Of-God">Lamb Of God</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mastodon">Mastodon</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Alice-In-Chains">Alice In Chains</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halestorm">Halestorm</a> , recent <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">Grammy</a> -winners <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a> and more.</p><p> Elsewhere, Corgan recently said <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-thinks-smashing-pumpkins-are-one-of-the-most-misunderstood-bands-in-the-history-of-rock-n-roll-3843962">he thinks the group are “one of the most misunderstood bands in the history of rock &#39;n&#39; roll”</a> , and has complained that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-addresses-claims-he-created-the-landscape-for-bands-like-muse-3840930">he does not “get the credit” for creating a musical landscape that allowed for the emergence of bands like Muse</a> .</p><p> Friends of Corgan, meanwhile, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgans-friends-convinced-hes-bill-burrs-half-brother-theyre-like-you-need-a-dna-test-3844501">are “convinced” that he and Bill Burr are half-brothers</a> and are urging him to get a DNA test.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smashing-pumpkins-announce-orchestral-chicago-residency-for-mellon-collie-and-the-infinite-sadness-30th-anniversary-3845459">The Smashing Pumpkins announce orchestral Chicago residency for &#39;Mellon Collie And The Infinite Sadness&#39; 30th anniversary</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
