oked Wing&#39; with gothic Caroline Polachek collaboration &#39;Industrial Love Song&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/These-New-Puritans-Caroline-Polachek-01-please-credit-Holly-Whittaker-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/These-New-Puritans-Caroline-Polachek-01-please-credit-Holly-Whittaker-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/These-New-Puritans-Caroline-Polachek-01-please-credit-Holly-Whittaker-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/These-New-Puritans-Caroline-Polachek-01-please-credit-Holly-Whittaker-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/These-New-Puritans-Caroline-Polachek-01-please-credit-Holly-Whittaker-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/These-New-Puritans-Caroline-Polachek-01-please-credit-Holly-Whittaker-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/These-New-Puritans-Caroline-Polachek-01-please-credit-Holly-Whittaker-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/these-new-puritans">These New Puritans</a> have announced their new album &#39;Crooked Wing&#39; and shared its lead single &#39;Industrial Love Song&#39;, featuring <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caroline-polachek">Caroline Polachek</a> . </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1014" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/these-new-puritans-inside-rose-album-review-2465501"><b>这些新清教徒 - “玫瑰之内”评论</b></a></li></ul><p>It will be the Southend band&#39;s first studio record in six years and the follow-up to 2019&#39;s &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/these-new-puritans-inside-rose-album-review-2465501">Inside The Rose</a> &#39;. It will be released on May 23 via Domino, and is available to pre-order/pre-save <a href="https://tnp.ffm.to/crookedwing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> in multiple formats, including digital, CD and vinyl.</p><p>他们以“工业情歌”的形式为粉丝们提供了专辑的第一个品味，该曲目发现了两个起重机互相唱歌。乐队的杰克·巴内特（Jack Barnett）从一个角度唱歌，而客座歌手Polachek代表另一个。</p><p>观看艺术家和摄影师Harley Weir与乐队一起观看歌曲的视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="这些新的清教徒 - 工业情歌[以卡罗琳·波拉切克（Caroline Polachek）为特色]（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZZ-MWiFgIzs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>巴内特解释说：“工业情歌是建筑工地上两个起重机之间的二重奏。” “卡罗琳（Caroline）唱着一辆起重机的一部分，我唱另一只起重机；他们无法触摸（他们的动作由操作员控制），但是当太阳升起时，他们希望他们的阴影会越过。我喜欢乔治如何提出误导期望的标题 - 这不是那种工业。”</p><p>乔治·巴内特（George Barnett）补充说：“很难将这首歌附加在一起。” “这是由已经存在数百年的乐器制作的进步音乐。”</p><p>杰克继续说：“当我们退出机械时代时，您会意识到我们与机器有多少共同点，它们的人有多共同。” “突然，从他们的角度写一首情歌并不是如此荒谬。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHDwbTdIXf-/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius