py-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Poppy-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Poppy-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Poppy">Poppy</a> took over <em>Jimmy Kimmel Live!</em>昨晚（3月10日），表现出色，表现为“放弃的成本”。</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/poppy-interview-negative-spaces-jordan-fish-3812948">Poppy cranks up the heaviness: “Sitting amongst the extremes feels very whole to me”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位金属歌手登上了舞台 - 戴着白色蓬松的连衣裙和红色手套，上面装饰着雾和一片花。 The performance sees her delicately sing the song and then transform towards the end with her loud blistering vocals screaming: <em>“Can&#39;t push me further down in the trench / Back against the wall / So you wanna test me now?/ While the others beg and fail to repent / They were fit to suffer / And I will dig back out,”</em> during the song&#39;s breakdown.</p><p> &#39;The Cost Of Giving Up&#39; was featured on Poppy&#39;s latest LP &#39;Negative Spaces&#39;. <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/poppy-interview-negative-spaces-jordan-fish-3812948">Previously speaking to <em>NME</em> about the album</a> , she shared: “I feel this record is some of the heaviest [work] that I&#39;ve done, but it&#39;s also the most saccharine and sweet. There&#39;s a feeling I get, when I&#39;m sitting amongst the extremes, that feels very whole to me.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Poppy – The Cost Of Giving Up" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-DOdPWmT5_o?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Her performance on <em>Jimmy Kimmel Live!</em> comes after she <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-knocked-loose-and-poppys-epic-jimmy-kimmel-live-performance-3816501">appeared as a guest during Knocked Loose&#39;s performance on the show</a> back in December. She joined the US hardcore punk group for a ferocious rendition of their collaborative single <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-knocked-loose-and-poppy-crushing-new-single-suffocate-3749930">&#39;Suffocate&#39;.</a> The former also performed some other tracks from their third and latest album, 2024&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/knocked-loose-announce-new-album-and-share-single-blinding-faith-3593739">&#39;You Won&#39;t Go Before You&#39;re Supposed To&#39;</a> .</p><p> The epic TV appearance included blazing pyro, circle pits in the wild crowd, and next-level screaming from both Garris and Poppy. Knocked Loose played the hard-hitting and riff-heavy song in front of the audience as rain poured down at the outdoor venue.</p><p> Knocked Loose frontman Bryan Garris previously addressed the criticism and other similar complaints they received following their performance on social media, writing: “The other day Knocked Loose performed on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/jimmykimmellive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@jimmykimmellive</a> . For a long time now our goal has been to see how far we could squeeze this band into places where we don&#39;t fit and I think this may be the biggest one. National television.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Knocked Loose ft. Poppy – Suffocate" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AYeDnOLfl0g?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Garris continued: “It feels like the ceiling gets higher for EVERYONE, every single day. We celebrate this together.太感谢了。</p><p> “Walking down the hallway as we were escorted to [the] stage I&#39;m looking to my left and right and seeing photos of all the celebrities that have been on the show over the years. Presidents, actors, musicians etc. I leaned over to [guitarist Isaac Hale] and said &#39;this started in your garage&#39;. He grabbed onto me and squeezed as hard as he could. That&#39;s a moment I&#39;ll never forget.”  Garris signed off: “PS if it scared you, good.”</p><p> In other Poppy news, the singer <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-poppys-tantalising-cover-of-sabrina-carpenters-taste-for-like-a-version-3835821">recently covered Sabrina Carpenter&#39;s &#39;Taste&#39; for Triple J&#39;s &#39;Like A Version&#39;</a> . She also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/poppy-launches-new-hello-i-am-poppy-t-shirt-after-courtney-laplante-mix-up-at-grammys-3835395">released a t-shirt poking fun at a mix-up with Spiritbox&#39;s Courtney LaPlante at the Grammys 2025</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-poppy-return-to-kimmel-with-blistering-the-cost-of-giving-up-performance-3845435">Watch Poppy return to &#39;Kimmel&#39; with blistering &#39;The Cost Of Giving Up&#39; performance</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
